{"tid":1689080,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"全部人同我一人一信寄去消防處！！！","createTime":"2019-11-02T16:21:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T05:15:24.000Z","uid":194241,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"9790b691ecc7a7a9d04013d3875542848856b440","tid":1689080,"uid":194241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:21:35.000Z","msg":"上網搵到份draft，大家可以參考下<br />\n一定要表揚個位消防員，唔可以比班狗踩住上 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果有其他更好既版本都可以放上黎<br />\n大家寄信又好，email都好<br />\n班仆街藍絲玩投訴，我地就要高度表揚<br />\n消防員，反抗！<br />\n唔撚係繼續比狗踩住上嘛？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n消防高層email：<br />\ndfs@hkfsd.gov.hk, ddfs@hkfsd.gov.hk, hkfsdenq@hkfsd.gov.hk, hkfsdenq@hkfsd.gov.hk, kw_fstn@hkfsd.gov.hk<br />\n<br />\n消防處處長李建日先生、副處長梁偉雄先生、分區指揮官(港島中)湯忠偉先生、消防區長(港島中) 楊啟宏先生、港灣消防局局長劉宇傑先生：<br />\n<br />\n2019年11月2日約晚上7時半，有警員一度向停泊路邊消防車（F328）發射催淚彈，並命中該部消防車。車上消防員慘中催淚煙，但仍然盡忠職守，全力保護消防車。他下車與在場數十名防暴警理論，雙方發生口角。網上有影片拍攝全個過程（<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/leoball727/videos/498401254078967/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fleoball727%2Fvideos%2F498401254078967%2F&d=5AUjfk%2BhgFT%2FKzSacqcGpEXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=0dc43396\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/leoball727/videos/498401254078967/</a> ），影片所見防暴警大力將該名消防員推向牆邊，並以粗言穢語責罵該名消防員。<br />\n<br />\n至於網上有傳言：「「F328 港灣消防局升降台 相信片中嗰位消防係該車司機 一嚟就用粗口問候伙記&rdquo;𨳒你 射撚到我架消防車 有無搞撚錯&rdquo; 行為明顯影響部門聲譽之餘 亦影響警察執行職務」絕非事實。<br />\n<br />\n此外， 該名消防員在如此混亂的環境仍然盡忠職守，留守現場戒備，並全力保護消防車，實在應該值得表揚。可惜，網上有傳言當該名消防員返回消防局，立即被高層傳召予以譴責，並褫奪未來升職機會。本人請問此傳言是否屬實？<br />\n<br />\n謝謝。<br />\n<br />\n香港市民 xxx 敬上"},{"pid":"b2f3331c48f2f5609dae32db25e47ca5de003863","tid":1689080,"uid":194241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:22:08.000Z","msg":"推呀！"},{"pid":"fce699dda8a661bff82f8a5643aad653d7ccd204","tid":1689080,"uid":194241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:23:37.000Z","msg":"表揚呀！"},{"pid":"3af02bef90886a36d4158eaea75572900470a70a","tid":1689080,"uid":194241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:24:16.000Z","msg":"唔好比班狗同藍絲得逞呀！！"},{"pid":"19dd862c130c6e3fe7f06a4bcbc8b02891343528","tid":1689080,"uid":194241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:25:25.000Z","msg":"支持消防！"},{"pid":"d0f5befa92e321fa7ea61153719457251b0dec3c","tid":1689080,"uid":333514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:26:08.000Z","msg":"高度表揚消防員，反抗！"},{"pid":"e7cff30a03d469bc4d7de5b78797d989a631ecbd","tid":1689080,"uid":238061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:26:24.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"f34a84a1f4107426c0584d2dac338af54358497c","tid":1689080,"uid":20076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:27:04.000Z","msg":"表揚呀"},{"pid":"83110836982eb5eb75ebe594d3867bc706d9c976","tid":1689080,"uid":194241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:27:27.000Z","msg":"表揚呀呀呀呀呀！！！"},{"pid":"11fd6be14be49adc49c649ae4b6b931e0362c0d9","tid":1689080,"uid":312859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:28:02.000Z","msg":"推,去信表揚等佢升職"},{"pid":"b6c70e75231a0a982d7204ac060e756fb7aef9e0","tid":1689080,"uid":194241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:28:44.000Z","msg":"推到佢升職呀屌！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cec425d37cf553f4695bede176b84e30bdb7938","tid":1689080,"uid":84277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:29:29.000Z","msg":"組織消防罷工"},{"pid":"d37b2f2426b429d053a8abed11aeb9a95c584682","tid":1689080,"uid":15195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:30:06.000Z","msg":"腥突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89aed6f4478980dc8866bf83a689fc149e4c076b","tid":1689080,"uid":194241,"like":0,"d